    "description": "<p>You can spend <strong>2 AP</strong> to censure all creatures of your choice who can see or hear you within 5 Spaces.</p><p>Make a Spell Attack against each target’s AD, and each target makes a Repeated Mental Save against your Save DC.</p><p><strong>Attack Hit:</strong> The target takes 1 Divine Damage.</p><p><strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target becomes Intimidated by you for 1 minute or until it takes damage again.</p>",
